Today, I was at a Post Office in Sunset Park to say #DontMessWithUSPS. 
@realdonaldtrump is trying to gut the Postal Service to advance his political agenda. 

We won't let that happen. This Saturday, the U.S. House will vote to protect this vital service. My full statement: https://t.co/77HXGQqmqe

Under the bill, lenders would need to make additional information readily available to borrowers including: 

-the annual percentage rate; 
-financing charges for loans; 
-loan terms; payment amounts and 
-collateral requirements.
