I stand with @RepAOC in condemning the sexist remarks made against her. 

They are an offense to all women. 

@RepTedYoho must truly apologize. https://t.co/wfw8bqB8ib

This language is insulting not just to @RepAOC but to all women. It's unbecoming of a Member of Congress and regardless of policy differences, wholly unacceptable. Members of Congress can always disagree, but do so agreeably.

@RepTedYoho - apologize. 

